cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.SI, cs.LG 

The paper deals with image deblurring and denoising, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and information theory (cs.IT). The use of wavelets for noise reduction and self-organizing maps for deblurring are also techniques commonly used in multimedia processing (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of SAR images, which are often studied in signal processing (cs.SI).
